Everyone needs a helper to assist in a day to day life. Unfortunately none of the physical personal tasks can be done without our involvment.
But there are many other tasks we can outsource to a trusted person. Again it is almost next to impossible to find a trusted person that
knows our things and do our tasks. So we need a person who knows us and help us doing our daily tasks. As we cannot trust any person
so let's try with a device/software who can do things perfect and trust worthy.

Contributors welcome!
